      • SpectraWithPrecursorMass

        public SpectraWithPrecursorMass(Table table,
                        int rowID,
                        double precursorMass,
                        java.lang.String spectra)
        Constructs a SpectraWithPrecursorMass object. The only difference between a Spectra and a SpectraWithPrecursorMass is that a SpectraWithPrecursorMass includes the PrecursorMass.
        参数:
        table - the corresponding SpectraWithPrecursorMassTable for this object
        rowID - the rowID in the SpectraWithPrecursorMassTable.
        precursorMass - the precursor mass of the spectra itself.
        spectra - a space-seperated String representation of a single fragmentation spectra.
